  <datafield tag="520" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
    <subfield code="a">We present a formalism for analysing redshift distortions based on a spherical harmonic expansion of the density field. We use a maximum likelihood estimator for the combination of density and bias parameters, $\Omega^0.6/b$. We test the method with $N$-body simulations and apply it to the 1.2 Jy IRAS redshift survey.</subfield>
